                        <p>You'll receive feedback on specific assignments throughout the teaching term, with a 'Semester One' report produced in the middle of the semester. Then, a report will be produced relating to the marks you received at the end of Semester One, and then a final report at the end of Semester Two.</p>
<p>In total, you'll receive three reports on your progress at INTO Newcastle. To help you with any difficulties, you'll receive one-to-one counselling on your grades and progression options with your Personal Tutor – with the support of the Student Progression and Placement Manager who will get to know you during your studies.</p>

